            <p>
               <milestone n="1" unit="line"/>[... as soon as I received your] letter, I have quickly collected [...] to a total of 110 stonecutters and I have written to you. You have denied, though, [...] by those in your command and to Ankyron Polis, [...] 
               <milestone n="4" unit="line"/>and now I have sent for them to come as many as [... out of] greediness, [...] reproach our men with laziness [...] 
               <milestone n="6" rend="break" unit="line"/>Verso: To Kleon.
               <note>Translation with slight modifications: B. Van Beek in P.Petr.Kleon, p. 123, © Peeters</note>
